  "texts": [
    "Volumes with framewise displacement higher than 0.3 mm were regressed out.",
    "Although smoothed time series were available, our analysis did not consider them.",
    "All specific steps were common to all subjects, both control and brain tumor patients.",
    "All images (T1s, T1 segmentations, diffusion, lesion masks and functional) were eventually co-registered to MNI space for comparison.",
    "Assessment of default mode network and tumoral BOLD Signals BOLD signals belonging to the DMN were identified with the Gordon functional Parcellation 77."
